- M1 )2 for Group 1 and SSE2 = 
(X   
- M2 )2 for Group 2  
3. Compute SSE = SSE1 + SSE2  
4. Compute df = N - 2 where N = n1 + n2  
5. Compute MSE = SSE/df  
6. Find t from a t table.  
7. Compute 
(If   
the sample sizes are equal then nh = n1 = n2).  
8. Compute 
  
9. Lower limit = Md - t 
  
10. Upper limit = Md + t 
  
11. Lower limit 
